ivestock and poultry, build structures, fish, gather mushrooms, berries and more. Life in a village won't let you get bored!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800460/extras/2494fbd975e31ed867b4683dfbd6aa27.poster.avif?t=1745946268\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800460/extras/2494fbd975e31ed867b4683dfbd6aa27.webm?t=1745946268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800460/extras/2494fbd975e31ed867b4683dfbd6aa27.mp4?t=1745946268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>- Social Interaction:</i> Every inhabitant has different needs, desires and dreams. Create a society where everyone can find their place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800460/extras/912b7ad1979ebb8f5afbaa1f70e411bf.poster.avif?t=1745946268\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800460/extras/912b7ad1979ebb8f5afbaa1f70e411bf.webm?t=1745946268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800460/extras/912b7ad1979ebb8f5afbaa1f70e411bf.mp4?t=1745946268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Russian Village Simulator on Mars combines your fantasies of space and your love of earth into an incredibly detailed and vibrant world. Build your Martian dream village!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you ready to take on the challenge and create a new legacy in the most unusual colony on Mars?</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
